            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2499255668978798939.png",
                "id": "talent3581",
                "key": "Water Ball",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Water Ball"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. The target character receives <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Refraction</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Refraction</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this card is attached switches to another character:</span> Elemental Dice Cost +1.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (R</span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">ounds): 2</span><br>(Only one such status can be applied on the same side at a time)</p><p></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/2b72995c4a7d257472864199056edd68_384750780998656538.png",
                "id": "talent91938",
                "key": "Influx Blast",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Influx Blast"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 5 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/04/248396185/57d2f05c0e87c6021cd6e4bfb5b031c1_7894775549814609458.png",
                "id": "talent31166",
                "key": "Rippled Reflection",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rippled Reflection"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/12/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_3497420098457790883.png",
